      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"bridging\" sounds a bit optimistic though. If those two groups have fundamentally different ideas about what a woman is—one based on biology and one based on identity—isn't it true that the \"consensus\" in academia and medicine is basically just picking one side over the other?",
